# Platform UI

## Layout and nav

- Role layouts: `apps/platform/src/app/(admin|advertiser|publisher)/`
- Sidebar config: `src/components/layout/nav-config.ts`
- Reuse shared primitives: `PageSection`, role heroes, Shadcn UI, Tailwind v4.

## Advertiser autoresponder (`/advertiser/email`)

Module layout: `app/(advertiser)/advertiser/email/layout.tsx` + `autoresponder-sub-nav.tsx`.

| Piece | Path |
|-------|------|
| Shell | `components/advertiser/email/email-module-shell.tsx` |
| Toolbar / stats / empty | `email-module-toolbar.tsx`, `email-module-stats.tsx`, `email-empty-state.tsx` |
| Mock data (UI-only) | `email-mock-data.ts` |
| Panels | `components/advertiser/email/panels/*-panel.tsx` |

Routes: dashboard, subscribers, lists, segments, tags, templates, campaigns, automations, sequences, forms, analytics, logs, suppression, settings.

Redirects: `/contacts` → `/subscribers`, `/activity` → `/logs`, `/smtp` → `/advertiser/email` (SMTP is admin-only at `/admin/settings`).

New email screens: wrap content in `EmailModuleShell`, add panel + page route, register in `autoresponder-sub-nav.tsx`. Use mock data until backend exists; do not add advertiser SMTP UI.

## Design tokens

Primary `#2563EB`, secondary `#14B8A6`, background `#F8FAFC`, cards `#FFFFFF`. Details in `docs/DESIGN-SYSTEM.md`.
